displayName: Ammos, the Desert City - Cooking Venue

parameters:
Wealthy gentleman: Don't you think that breaking through
the traditional taste with ingenuity is what a chef should
strive for?

Traveling Goods Merchant: It's so hot, I wish I could drink
wine with Fotizona and not be able to resist.

Meek girl: Do you know about the secret cooking battle? I
wonder what kind of intense battle can be seen.

Traveling Goods Merchant: It's so hot, I wish I could drink
wine with Fotizona and not be able to resist.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Owner, Tokyo. 'Aren't you Meri!? Haha, Actina didn't
abandon me.'

Chef Meri: I want to repay the favor I received by testing
if my cooking skills are up to par, but only half of it.

Owner, Tokyo. 'I'm amazed by your passion for cooking, Clea
and the others have also been kind enough to help.'

Clea: I've taken care of the Coriba matter. Now all that's
left is for you to win the cooking showdown.

Chef Meri: It all depends on our skills, Owner Tokyo! I'll
go ahead and do a preliminary inspection of the cooking
venue.
Owner Tokyo: Do you think this is the end for you?

Clea: The opponent who has been moving meticulously. There
is no doubt that there are still sabotage operations.

Owner Tokyo: I'm sorry, but I want you all to come and help
as well.
Clea: Understood. I will let you know when I am ready.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Owner, Tokyo, I expect you to be prepared without
hesitation. Please call me after you have made sufficient
preparations.
Clea: No problem, I'm ready anytime.
Owner, Tokyo, Understood, let's go too.
